{"tid":773944,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"[求意見-9月東京]做孝子帶母親6日遊","createTime":"2018-08-10T02:49:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-10T12:10:05.000Z","uid":34550,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"876ff165e016fc758907d39dd26a75a1e00d0247","tid":773944,"uid":34550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T02:49:30.000Z","msg":"9月中準備同家母去東京玩6日，EXPEDIA 揀左住池袋對上板橋果邊。<br />\n初步PLAN左個行程，求評，求好西介紹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\nDay 1  1700 到成田  --&gt; 酒店CHECKIN  --&gt; 東京巨蛋食晚飯  --&gt; 酒店<br />\nDay 2  築地 --&gt; 東京鐵塔 --&gt; 台場<br />\nDay 3  鐮倉 --&gt;  江之島 --&gt; 新宿晚餐<br />\nDay 4  築地 --&gt; 淺草雷門 --&gt; 新者御宛 --&gt; 明治神宮 --&gt; 涉谷/六本木 晚餐<br />\nDay 5  橫濱 --&gt; 遊船河 --&gt; 山下公園/山手異人館 --&gt; 中華街 --&gt; 紅磚倉庫 --&gt; 合味道博物館 --&gt; 港未來21<br />\nDay 6 秋葉原電器街 --&gt; 上野阿美橫町 --&gt; 上野動物園(有時間先去) --&gt; 1600 京成上野去機場。"},{"pid":"6c60792ea3feaa2f0456297f871cdb1c14e449e7","tid":773944,"uid":34550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T06:23:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"626156760f269c22aedec3d6d729e6fa5c5647a7","tid":773944,"uid":94978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T06:39:04.000Z","msg":"家母幾大？<br />\n自己揸車？<br />\n行程對老人家會唔會太chur<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0718474a64ddff65f6c21e3616be116352e03df","tid":773944,"uid":34550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"626156760f269c22aedec3d6d729e6fa5c5647a7","tid":773944,"uid":94978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T06:39:04.000Z","msg":"家母幾大？<br />\n自己揸車？<br />\n行程對老人家會唔會太chur<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T07:15:48.000Z","msg":"50到尾60啦，邊D會太CHUR??<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img 